{"tid":2198004,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"P牌學車好日子！安全行車日","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T06:32:47.000Z","uid":231886,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0437e2fd912a3f0433c5b0cf3e07e8edd83ababd","tid":2198004,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"咁多個學車地點，最好行一定係天光道，除左有寧靜環境，仲有未死哂嘅香港法治座落係九龍城裁判法院，而對面就係好留意安全駕駛的黑警同狗屋！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9Doh64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9Doh64.jpg&h=62b1b046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收到風<span class=\"red\">下星期二，9月15日</span>好似有個<span class=\"red\">新巴司機被落案起訴「不小心駕駛」</span>。<br />\n各位學神好似咁岩星期二會去呢段路，司機大佬千其唔好去亞皆老街同太子道西、司機大佬千其唔好去亞皆老街同太子道西、司機大佬千其唔好去亞皆老街同太子道西 ！果到好多巴士、小巴、私家車，仲有好大個迴旋處。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果你經過九龍城裁判法院</span>，最好安全車速啦！即係<span class=\"red\">30km／hr </span>！因為呢條路有黑警MON得好緊，就算你<span class=\"red\">塞車</span>都唔好<span class=\"red\">響鞍</span>！無故響鞍一定拉你，實捉到你呀！"},{"pid":"69896c405536a1132a88923dd02ec3600e0f80e0","tid":2198004,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"誰偷偷留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a32ab59b08cbd4394a65109e6ad2f0e4309bdc","tid":2198004,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"30km/h 係學神揸3波比的士狗推車既速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797c5ac96d6e12eaf04387b0fa9c8a777c40c094","tid":2198004,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6a32ab59b08cbd4394a65109e6ad2f0e4309bdc","tid":2198004,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"30km/h 係學神揸3波比的士狗推車既速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci